title: Free Agent EDGE, DL, OL Rankings, Coronavirus forces NFL to cancel owners meetings (Football 3/13)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco as Free Agency Preview Week concludes. But first, the guys have to address how coronavirus continues to impact the NFL including the cancellation of the owners meetings scheduled for later this month (1:00). Will and Pete also analyze how COVID-19 could influence the NFL Draft. Next, a look at free agency with rankings of the Top 5 edge rushers (14:00) and defensive (20:00) and offensive (25:30) lineman with a focus on their best potential landing spots.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
